    <h2>The Program</h2>
    <p>
      <em>Stratos</em> campaigns primarily single-handed and double-handed offshore distance racing on the US Northeast Coast.
      The offshore program centers on the Bermuda Race, Annapolis to Newport, Bermuda 1-2, Block Island Race, and the Vineyard Race.
      Crewed inshore racing runs out of Cedar Point Yacht Club and neighboring clubs on Long Island Sound.
    </p>

    <h2>Sails</h2>
    <p>North Sails and Evolution Sails inventory includes a J0 and asymmetrical spinnakers: A1.5, A2, A3, A4.</p>

    <h2>Owner / Driver</h2>
    <p>Marcus Wunderlich — Cedar Point Yacht Club, 15 years racing.</p>
